## 4. Security Layer Flow

### Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[ApiClient] --> B[Dio Instance]
    B --> C[ApiSecurityInterceptor]
    C --> D{Is offline?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Reject with ConnectionError]
    D -->|No| F{Is sensitive endpoint?}
    F -->|Yes| G{RSA key ready?}
    G -->|No| H[fetchAndCachePublicKey]
    H --> I[Load from SecureStorage or fetch from server]
    G -->|Yes| J[Encrypt sensitive fields via EncryptionService.encryptJson]
    F -->|No| K[Pass through]
    J --> L{Path contains /auth/?}
    K --> L
    L -->|Yes| M[Skip Authorization header]
    L -->|No| N[Inject Bearer token from SecureStorageService]
    M --> O[Send request]
    N --> O

    O --> P{Response 401?}
    P -->|Yes| Q[Attempt silent token refresh]
    Q -->|Success| R[Retry original request with new token]
    Q -->|Failure| S[SessionManager.logout → redirect to login]
    P -->|No| T[Return response]
```

### Files Involved

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| [api_interceptor.dart](file:///d:/Git/SIP/lib/core/security/api_interceptor.dart) | Central request/response/error interceptor |
| [encryption_service.dart](file:///d:/Git/SIP/lib/core/security/encryption_service.dart) | RSA-OAEP-SHA256 encryption of sensitive fields |
| [secure_storage_service.dart](file:///d:/Git/SIP/lib/core/security/secure_storage_service.dart) | flutter_secure_storage wrapper for tokens, keys, flags |
| [app_config.dart](file:///d:/Git/SIP/lib/core/config/app_config.dart) | Encrypted endpoints + sensitive fields lists |
| [secure_logger.dart](file:///d:/Git/SIP/lib/core/security/secure_logger.dart) | Redacted logging (strips sensitive values) |

### Encrypted Endpoints

```
auth/generate-otp     auth/verify-otp     auth/register
savings/initiate      savings/check-eligibility
submit-kyc            update-kyc          kyc/upload
withdraw              verify-upi          verify-bank
payment               investment
mpin/create           mpin/validate       mpin/change       mpin/reset
```

### Sensitive Fields (Encrypted Before Transmission)

```
password    otp    login_pin    transaction_pin    mpin    old_mpin    new_mpin
aadhaar_number    pan_number    pan    bank_account_number    account_no
ifsc_code    upi_id    kyc_details    withdrawal_amount    payment_details
amount    amount_inr    payment_pin    bank_details    mobile    weight    buy_rate
```

### Security Assessment

| Check | Status | Notes |
|-------|--------|-------|
| RSA-OAEP-SHA256 encryption | ✅ | Using `pointycastle` + `encrypt` packages |
| No hardcoded secret keys | ✅ | Public key fetched from `crypto/public-key` endpoint |
| Key cached in secure storage | ✅ | Via `SecureStorageService.saveServerPublicKey()` |
| Offline detection blocks requests | ✅ | `connectivity_plus` check in `onRequest` |
| Silent token refresh on 401 | ✅ | Retries original request transparently |
| Logout on refresh failure | ✅ | Calls `SessionManager.logout()` |
| Recursive field encryption | ✅ | `encryptJson()` handles nested maps and lists |
| Base URL uses HTTP | ❌ | **`http://startgoldapi.logimaxindia.com`** — Must use HTTPS in production |

