### ✅ Strengths

| # | Strength | Details |
|---|----------|---------|
| **S1** | RSA key management | Dynamic key exchange, no hardcoded secrets, cached in secure storage |
| **S2** | Silent token refresh | 401 → auto-refresh → retry; seamless UX |
| **S3** | Recursive field encryption | Handles nested JSON + arrays properly |
| **S4** | MPIN security | Shuffled keypad, 5-attempt lockout, screenshot protection, biometric gating |
| **S5** | Withdrawal requires manual MPIN | No biometric shortcut for financial operations |
| **S6** | Root detection at startup | Blocks compromised devices entirely |
| **S7** | Offline detection | Prevents failed requests from polluting UX |
| **S8** | Rate locking system | Prevents rate manipulation between screens |
| **S9** | Secure logging | `SecureLogger` redacts sensitive data from all log output |
